         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>To Theodoros, strategos [of the Arsinoite nome, Herakleides division], from Gaius Iulius [Niger, Antinoite], landholder at Karanis in the [division of Herakleides, about] 52 years of age. [- - -] certain persons dug their way through the wall of the courtyard like thieves and [- - -] drove off two donkeys of mine, one a female, the other a male [- - -];(15 lines too fragmentary to be translated)</ab>
         </div>
